verbose_text: Genes both differentially expressed in the Eif6 +/- gastrocnemius muscle and correlated to the expression of Eif6 in the HERITAGE dataset were enriched with genes related to energy metabolism, including oxidative phosphorylation complexes (e.g., Atp5l, Ndufs4), mitochondrial function (e.g., Sod2, Gfm2), and glucose metabolism (e.g., Pdhb) (XREF_FIG).
